      ],
      "text": "Mortals whose ancestry has been influenced by archons are called lawbringers. They may have mortal ancestors who fought alongside archons against the forces of evil and entropy, or they may have been born from a union between an archon and a mortal. Many lawbringers seek adventure to bringing order to the world.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
